        <abstract>
            <p>Describes Patagonia and its inhabitants.</p>
            <p>Writes of his pleasure in geology.</p> 
<p>Predicts that Falklands will become an "important halting place". Outlines <hi rend="italic">Beagle</hi>’s future itinerary.</p> 
